      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  w-gch-oap-war.
      *            *---------------------------------------------------*
      *            * Numero giorni da evidenziare 0..7                 *
      *            *---------------------------------------------------*
               10  w-gch-oap-war-nge      pic  9(02)                  . 
      *            *---------------------------------------------------*
